What's the weather like where you live
I currently live in Ho Chi Minh City, which has a typical tropical climate. The weather is warm year-round, with two distinct seasons: the dry season and the rainy season. Interestingly, even during the dry months, occasional rain showers can still occur.
I personally prefer the rainy season because the temperature tends to be milder, usually around 25 degress celcius. It feels much more comfortable and refreshing compared to the intense heat during the dry season.
